reviewText: Product as described.  Good transaction.  Thanks...

Bought several volumes to make a collection for the grandkids on  DVDs. They seem to enjoy them as much as I did when I was little.  I named one of my daughters after Karen and my grandkids appear to feel a connection :)

Filmed several years ago (before MS began talking an obvious toll on her health), Annette shares her rise to stardom with excerpts from the MMC and later. One of the few opportunities of seeing her in later years.
